<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Ersame liebe fraw, uns hat <expan cert="unknown">H.</expan> Pfifferling
                <expan>ein<ex>en</ex></expan> brief <expan>newlich<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gesant, des
            wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> ein <expan>abschr<ex>ift</ex></expan>
<expan>hierinn<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>versloss<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>schik<ex>en</ex></expan>. Nu <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir
                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nome<ex>n</ex></expan>, wie <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan>
            Pfifferling ewr <expan>dien<ex>er</ex></expan> sey. <expan>Daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> so
                <expan>bitt<ex>en</ex></expan> wir ewr <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> mit fleiss,
            ir wellet <expan>dens<ex>elben</ex></expan> Pfifferling daran weisen und
                <expan>halte<ex>n</ex></expan>, daz er sölich abklag abtu und mit uns noch den
                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> niht args zu schiken hab, als wir ewch des
                <expan>sunderl<ex>ich</ex></expan> wol getrawen. Dewht <expan>ab<ex>er</ex></expan>
            den <expan>vorg<ex>enante</ex>n</expan> Pfifferling, daz er zu
              <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex></expan> Luczen, <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>, <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> zu
              <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> den <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> icht zu sprechen
            hett, so <expan>well<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir im <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>scheinbott<ex>en</ex></expan> mit <expan>seine<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>voll<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gwalt <expan>frewntl<ex>ich</ex></expan>
<pb facs="#facs_73" id="35v"/>slewnigs <expan>reht<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>g<ex>er</ex>n</expan> von in <expan>helff<ex>en</ex></expan> vor des reichs
                <expan>richt<ex>er</ex></expan> bey uns zu <expan>Nur<ex>emberg</ex></expan>, wenn
            wir des ermant <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan>, so <expan>dies<ex>elben</ex></expan> die
                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>n</expan> zu den er zu sprechen hett anheim sein on geverd.
            Denn wo wir <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb oder dienst etc. Und lat uns
                <expan>daru<ex>m</ex>b</expan> ewr <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan> antwurt wider
                <expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan> bey disem <expan>botte<ex>n</ex></expan>.
                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> vi<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Katherine.</ab>
